This is unit++ (http://sourceforge.net/projects/unitpp/) with the addition of
Setup/Teardown on test, suite and global level.

To install it:

on Linux:
	autoreconf -isf .
	./configure
	make install
	
or:
	mkdir build$(uname -m)
	cd build$(uname -m)
	autoreconf -isf ..
	../configure
	make install
	
on Windows:
	open the project VS2008/unit++.vcproj in Visual Studio 2008 and compile
	
Running unit++'s unit tests on Linux:
	./unit++
